Package com.github.dandelion.datatables.jsp.tag

Class Summary
AbstractColumnTag Abstract class which contains : all the boring technical stuff needed by Java tags (setters for all Column tag attributes) helper methods used to manipulate the columns
AbstractTableTag Abstract class which contains : all the boring technical stuff needed by Java tags (setters for all Table tag attributes) helper methods used to init the table
CallbackTag Tag used to add DataTables' callbacks.
CaptionTag Tag used to generate a HTML table's caption.
ColumnHeadTag Tag used to custom the header of a table's column.
ColumnTag Tag used to generate a HTML table's column.
ExportTag Tag which allows to configure an export type for the current table.
ExtraConfTag Tag used to add some extra Javascript configuration to the DataTable.
ExtraFileTag Tag used to add an extra Javascript configuration file.
PropTag Tag used to locally override the Dandelion global configuration.
TableTag Tag used to generate a HTML table.
